item.title: CVE-2017-13102|2024-08-05T18:58:12.339Z -- gameloft -- asphalt%20xtreme%3A%20offroad%20rally%20racing
item.description: Gameloft Asphalt Xtreme: Offroad Rally Racing, 1.6.0, 2017-08-13, iOS application uses a hard-coded key for encryption. Data stored using this key can be decrypted by anyone able to access this key.
